# Frontend env vars (read at build time by Vite — must be set BEFORE `vite build`).
#
# The landing site AND the trial app are served from the SAME Railway deployment
# at https://synthèse.fr, so by default the frontend makes same-origin requests
# (empty base URL → relative paths like `/api/auth/start-anonymous-trial`).
#
# Only set this if you ever split the app onto a separate domain.

# VITE_TRIAL_API_BASE=https://app.synthese.fr
